e":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"根本就係回港易播毒 個臭閪又死唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e841fb420e0f6b550103294b71befed4aaf759","tid":2313812,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"推爆佢老母"},{"pid":"b289af12b0a9e75417414198e950d2f2da59d0ba","tid":2313812,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NqUfNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NqUfNA.jpg&h=8ecd401b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為支國唔撚比<span class=\"red\">慶祝</span><br />\n所以連續三日過千隻支人來港慶祝性旦<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">回港易病毒</span></span>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"201fb32f481da4d1d34dd211e1e7514a5ac15d22","tid":2313812,"uid":70964,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T00:59:21.000Z","msg":"封左關林鄭點整死香港?"}}